Percentage of children of the official primary school age who are in school. The vertical axis shows estimates from
administrative data on enrollment. The horizontal axis shows estimates from household survey data on attendance.
Figures correspond to most recent year with available data.
Net primary-school attendance rate based on household survey data
Net primary-school enrollment rate based on administrative data
Source: UNESCO (via World Bank); Demographic and Health Surveys (DHS)
